OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson was at the
OL,7,Fheight of his long political career
OL,8,Fwhen police officers knocked on his
OL,9,Fdoor early in the morning on March 28
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FTwo months previously the DUP leader
OL,13,Fhad led his party back into the
OL,14,Fdevolved institutions at Stormont,
OL,15,Fhaving struck a deal with the UK
OL,16,Fgovernment to end his two-year boycott
OL,17,Fof power sharing in Northern Ireland
OL,18,Fin protest at post-Brexit trading
OL,19,Farrangements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
