CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FThat Donaldson felt emboldened enough
OL,7,Fto face down intense criticism from
OL,8,Funionist rivals unconvinced of the
OL,9,Fsubstance of the Safeguarding the
OL,10,FUnion agreement was indicative of a
OL,11,Fpolitician confident in the authority
OL,12,Fhe wielded.
OL,14,FIt was arguably the zenith of his 40
OL,15,Fyears in politics. But then came the
OL,16,Ffall.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
