PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FWhen detectives arrived at his house
OL,7,Fin Dromore, Co Down, at 6am that
OL,8,Fmorning to arrest him over historical
OL,9,Fsexual offences everything he had
OL,10,Fbuilt across four decades in politics
OL,11,Fimploded.
OL,13,FWithin hours he had quit as DUP leader
OL,14,Fand was suspended from the party.
OL,16,FHe had assumed the leadership of the
OL,17,FDUP three years earlier after a
OL,18,Fchaotic period that saw Arlene Foster
OL,19,Fousted in an internal revolt, only for
OL,20,Fher successor Edwin Poots to suffer a
OL,21,Fsimilar fate weeks after taking over.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
