OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FDonaldson, who had been narrowly
OL,7,Fdefeated by Poots in the first
OL,8,Fleadership contest, was returned
OL,9,Funopposed. He was seen as a safe pair
OL,10,Fof hands who would bring stability to
OL,11,Fa party that had been rocked to its
OL,12,Fcore by a summer of upheaval.
OL,14,FBorn in Kilkeel in Co Down, Donaldson
OL,15,Fbegan his political career with the
OL,16,FUlster Unionist Party (UUP), joining
OL,17,Fin his late teens.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
