PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FHis policeman cousin Samuel Donaldson
OL,7,Fwas murdered by the IRA during the
OL,8,FTroubles and he often claimed that
OL,9,Fevent influenced his decision to enter
OL,10,Fpolitical life.
OL,12,FAt the age of 16, he continued a
OL,13,Ffamily tradition by becoming a member
OL,14,Fof the Orange Order, and later
OL,15,Ffollowed in the footsteps of his late
OL,16,Ffather Jim by joining the Ulster
OL,17,FDefence Regiment (UDR).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
