OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FIn the early 1980s, he worked as
OL,7,Fpersonal assistant for former
OL,8,FConservative cabinet minister and then
OL,9,FUUP MP Enoch Powell, running the
OL,10,Fveteran politician's election
OL,11,Fcampaigns.
OL,13,FIn 1985, aged 22, he was elected to a
OL,14,Fshort-lived incarnation of the
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland Assembly, becoming
OL,16,Fthe youngest person to win a seat at
OL,17,FStormont.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
