PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FHe became MP for Lagan Valley in 1997
OL,7,F` a seat he would hold continuously
OL,8,Funtil his forced exit from politics in
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FHe was also an Assembly member for the
OL,12,Fsame constituency from 2003 to 2010
OL,13,Fand a Lisburn councillor for six years
OL,14,Funtil 2011. He ultimately had to
OL,15,Fvacate the latter two roles and
OL,16,Fconcentrate on his work as an MP ahead
OL,17,Fof legislation being introduced to
OL,18,Fprevent politicians from so-called
OL,19,F"double-jobbing".
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/22
