OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FThrough the peace process in the 1990s
OL,7,FDonaldson became an increasingly
OL,8,Finfluential figure within the UUP and
OL,9,Fby 1998 ` the year of the historic
OL,10,FGood Friday Agreement ` he was a
OL,11,Fsenior member of the Ulster Unionists'
OL,12,Fnegotiating delegation.
OL,14,FHe famously walked out of those talks
OL,15,Fjust hours before the peace accord was
OL,16,Fstruck.
OL,18,FThe MP left Castle Buildings at
OL,19,FStormont in protest at what his party
OL,20,Fwas about to sign up to.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
