CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FArlene Foster was also in the Ulster
OL,7,FUnionist Party at the time and the
OL,8,Fpair became prominent members of a
OL,9,Ftight-knit hard-line faction within
OL,10,Fthe UUP that opposed the Good Friday
OL,11,FAgreement and questioned the direction
OL,12,Fof Mr Trimble's leadership.
OL,14,FIn late 2003 they sensationally quit
OL,15,Fthe party and weeks later defected to
OL,16,Fthe DUP.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/22
