OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FHe did serve a brief stint as a junior
OL,7,Fminister at Stormont the year before
OL,8,Fhis tenure as an MLA was cut short due
OL,9,Fto the looming double-jobbing law.
OL,11,FMs Foster, by contrast, operated at
OL,12,Fthe heart of devolved government in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland across that period,
OL,14,Ftaking on a range of ministerial roles
OL,15,Fbefore ultimately assuming the party
OL,16,Fleadership and becoming Northern
OL,17,FIreland's First Minister.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
