OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FDonaldson was appointed to the privy
OL,7,Fcouncil in 2007 and was recognised by
OL,8,Fthe late Queen in her 2016 Birthday
OL,9,FHonours and given a knighthood
OL,11,FIn 2009, he was caught up in the
OL,12,Fparliamentary expenses scandal and
OL,13,Fapologised for claiming for pay-to-
OL,14,Fview films during hotel stays in
OL,15,FLondon.
OL,17,FHe denied the films were adult in
OL,18,Fnature, insisting he paid to watch
OL,19,Fmovies like Star Wars and The Lion,
OL,20,FThe Witch And The Wardrobe.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/22
