OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FNevertheless, Donaldson repaid around
OL,7,F#600, acknowledging he was wrong to
OL,8,Fsubmit the claims.
OL,10,FOne occasion that did see him handed a
OL,11,Fleading part was in the post-general
OL,12,Felection shakedown of 2017 when Prime
OL,13,FMinister Theresa May found herself in
OL,14,Fneed of the DUP's support to form a
OL,15,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/22
