OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FThere was no inevitability about him
OL,7,Fever taking on the leadership of the
OL,8,FDUP, and prior to Ms Foster's dramatic
OL,9,Fdownfall in the summer of 2021 there
OL,10,Fwas a sense that any chance of him
OL,11,Flanding the top job had passed.
OL,13,FThat was underscored when he lost out
OL,14,Fto Mr Poots in the first leadership
OL,15,Frace.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
