CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FIt would later emerge that following
OL,7,Fthat defeat he held a secret meeting
OL,8,Fwith then Ulster Unionist leader Doug
OL,9,FBeattie, allegedly to scope out the
OL,10,Fpotential of returning to the UUP
OL,11,Ffold. Donaldson would deny that was
OL,12,Fthe purpose of the discussion.
OL,14,FThe encounter with Mr Beattie proved
OL,15,Fimmaterial, as events in the DUP
OL,16,Fleadership saga soon took another
OL,17,Funexpected twist when Mr Poots was
OL,18,Fforced to resign after only 21 days in
OL,19,Fcharge.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
