CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FDonaldson was handed a second chance
OL,7,Fto lead the party he was allegedly
OL,8,Fthinking of quitting only days earlier.
OL,10,FHe took the reins amid the protracted
OL,11,Ftumult over Brexit's Irish Sea border
OL,12,Fand intensifying unionist anger at
OL,13,Fchecks and inspections introduced on
OL,14,Fgoods moving from Great Britain into
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
