FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FIn February the following year,
OL,7,FDonaldson pulled DUP First Minister
OL,8,FPaul Givan out of the executive,
OL,9,Feffectively collapsing the
OL,10,Fpowersharing institutions. The bold
OL,11,Fmove was designed to heap pressure on
OL,12,Fthe UK government to take steps to cut
OL,13,Fpost-Brexit red tape.
OL,15,FThe stand-off would last for two years
OL,16,Fbefore Donaldson finally decided he
OL,17,Fhad secured enough concessions from
OL,18,Fthe Government to allow his party to
OL,19,Freturn to Stormont.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G19/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
