OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FIt was a high-risk play but one he
OL,7,Fappeared to have pulled off.
OL,9,FHe adopted an energetic approach to
OL,10,Fselling the deal to the public, making
OL,11,Fvarious confident claims about the
OL,12,Fsignificance of the measures he had
OL,13,Fextracted from No 10. They were claims
OL,14,Fthat the party would later concede had
OL,15,Fbeen oversold.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G20/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
