OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41821
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782317940
OL,3,CArrest of Donaldson came at the height
OL,4,Cof his political powers
OL,6,FNevertheless, as Easter approached in
OL,7,F2024, Donaldson seemed to have
OL,8,Fachieved his objective. The DUP had
OL,9,Freturned to government without any
OL,10,Fnotable revolt from the party
OL,11,Fgrassroots.
OL,13,FHe position as leader was secure,
OL,14,Fhaving taken the biggest gamble of his
OL,15,Fpolitical career.
OL,17,FAll that would change, and change in
OL,18,Fan instance, when the door knock came
OL,19,Fat 6am on Thursday March 28 2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G21/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
